item.title: Bobblehead Soccer Royale
item.description: Move your bobblehead soccer stars around the field. Kick the goals into the opponent’s goal. Collect the powerups to gain an edge over your opponents. Features: Mad physics that trumps realism Fun and vibrant soccer atmosphere Funny caricature expressions Challenge over 20+ top soccer players in the world Increasingly challenging levels. Get to Level 3 and the game really heats up. Forget FIFA World Cup, fans of puppet soccer fans will love this game.
